        "setup": "Go to Tableau Server or Tableau Cloud and create a Personal Access Token in your user settings. Tableau documents PATs as the recommended way to authenticate to the REST API and Metadata API. Keep the token secret; you’ll typically receive a token name and secret, and use them together to sign in and obtain the short-lived `X-Tableau-Auth` session token.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      },
      "tableau_username_password": {
